Copy the code now and enjoy your shopping, Don't forget to use your discount code at checkout!
（For Orders Over $1000)
B4-50W laser cuts metals up to 0.7mm thick with 0.01mm accuracy.
The laser source in the B4 50W Fiber Laser Engraver has an impressive lifespan of over 100,000 hours, ensuring you get long-lasting, consistent performance.
Every $4,000 Purchase, Unlocks FreeCutting Panel ($249 Value)
